claim.claim-text:
37. A method for applying a coating to a medical appliance comprising the steps of: 
placing the medical appliance in a supporting device; 
placing a first therapeutic agent into a first chamber connected to a bubble jet printing head; 
transporting the first therapeutic agent from the first chamber to the bubble jet printing head; 
moving the bubble jet printing head with respect to the medical appliance; and 
forcing the first therapeutic agent from the bubble jet printing head onto the medical appliance to form a first coating.
